text: Tumhi sanga, tumhi amacyababata jya gostincya pratikseta ahata, ti dona cangalya gostimpaiki eka ahe ani amhi tumacyababata ya gosticya pratikseta ahota ki ekatara allahane tumhala apalyatarphe ekhadi siksa dyavi kinva amacya hatuna, tevha eka bajula tumhi pratiksa kara, dusarya bajula amhi tumacyasobata pratiksa karita ahota
